      "end_timestamp": "2:56",
      "call_index": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "call1_25",
      "text": "Okay, this is with reference to your initial policy, sir. We have decided to go ahead with your proposal, but as a part of the process, we needed to conduct a video medical verification, sir, in which I will ask you some verification and medical history questions. This call will be recorded for company's audit and quality purpose. I will be asking you a few questions regarding your insurance application and this recorded call should take maximum 10 to 12 minutes of your time, sir.",
