      "start_timestamp": "3:21",
      "end_timestamp": "3:30",
      "call_index": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "call1_28",
      "text": "And if the proposal is accepted, it shall form of basis of legal contract of insurance between you and Tata AIA Life Insurance. Any incorrect, false statement replies could have an impact on the contract and may lead to cancellation of the policy before or after the insurance and may also lead to rejection of the claim later. You are hence records to respond thoughtfully and correctly.",
